-- Walt Disney Makes Open Offer for UTV in India Starting January
-- B y   K e t a k i   G o k h a l e
-- 2011-12-29T06:55:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-29/walt-disney-makes-open-offer-for-utv-in-india-starting-january.html
Walt Disney Co. (DIS)  offered to buy the
shares of India’s  UTV Software Communications Ltd. (UTV)  it doesn’t
own starting Jan. 16.  Disney offered to buy the stock from retail shareholders
for between 835.03 rupees and 1,000 rupees apiece, according to
an advertisement in the Economic Times newspaper yesterday. The
offer will close on Jan. 20. Disney already owns 50.44 percent
of UTV.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ketaki Gokhale in Mumbai at 
 kgokhale@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Michael Tighe at   mtighe4@bloomberg.net  